(2, 1, '2018-01-03 11:27:53', '2018-01-03 11:27:53', '<div class="container margin_60 padd_bottom_20">\r\n        <div class="main_title"><!--span--><h2>Downham Hall, Essex. A country hall in rolling countryside</h2>\r\n            <p></p>Currently preparing to open to the public with 2 rooms and our entire South Wing holiday rental. We\r\n            are based in Downham, Essex and only 40 minutes to London Liverpool Street station.\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="row">\r\n            <div class="col-md-4">\r\n                <div class="box_home"><i class="icon_set_2_icon-104"></i>\r\n                    <h3>Cozy and Charming rooms</h3>\r\n                    <p></p>We have generous spaces of rooms and are currently renovating them to include ensuites to go\r\n                    along with the period features.\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-4">\r\n                <div class="box_home"><i class="icon_set_2_icon-108"></i>\r\n                    <h3>Relax in a beautiful setting</h3>\r\n                    <p></p>Downham Hall is a fantastic historic home in a wonderfully secluded yet spacious plot\r\n                    surrounded on all sides by fields and the corresponding farm. We have a moat, swimming pool and\r\n                    great rolling fields.\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="col-md-4">\r\n                <div class="box_home"><i class="icon_set_1_icon-40"></i>\r\n                    <h3>Lots of local activities</h3>\r\n                    <p></p>Despite our rural location we are lucky to be close to so many activities and of course easy\r\n                    access to London opens up so much. We have listed a lot of these activities on our activities page.\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div><!-- End row--></div>\r\n        <div class="container add_bottom_60">\r\n            <div class="main_title add_bottom_45"><span></span>\r\n                <h2>Other stuff you may consider</h2>\r\n                <p>We have individual rooms to hire, our entire South Wing by the week and also our function spaces\r\n                    including indoor and outdoor options.</p></div>\r\n            <div class="row">\r\n                <div id="strip_activities" class="col-md-8">\r\n                    <ul>\r\n                        <li><img src="https://www.downhamhall.com/wp-content/themes/animatedone/img/activities_1_thumb.jpg" alt=""\r\n                                 class="img-circle styled"><h4>Take a\r\n                                walk</h4>There are public footpaths running very close to the property and many other\r\n                            walks not too much further afield. Here is the&nbsp;<a target="_blank"\r\n                                                                                   href="https://osmaps.ordnancesurvey.co.uk/osmaps/51.6283806920,0.5001563255,17">local\r\n                                ordnance survey map</a>&nbsp;to track local routes. Here is also a helpful page for a\r\n                            good route from the Church that faces the Hall -&nbsp;<a target="_blank"\r\n                                                                                     href="http://www.essexwalks.com/walks/downham.html#page=description">Essex\r\n                                Walks</a><br><br>Only a short 5 minute drive we also have Hanningfield reservoir which\r\n                            is great for shorter family walks with a nice cafe and plenty of parking<a\r\n                                    href="/activities" class="link_normal">Read more</a></li>\r\n                        <li><img src="https://www.downhamhall.com/wp-content/themes/animatedone/img/activities_2_thumb.jpg" alt=""\r\n                                 class="img-circle styled"><h4>Great for\r\n                                kids</h4>We are a family run business and actively welcome children and so understand\r\n                            the need to entertain them at times.\r\n                            Luckily we have some really good attractions locally due to the family friendly nature of\r\n                            Essex.\r\n                            Most notably we have Marsh Farm a short drive in South Woodham Ferrers. Primarily aimed at\r\n                            younger children but very well done and somewhere we used to travel with our kids to for an\r\n                            hour (when we lived in London). More info here&nbsp;<a target="_blank"\r\n                                                                                   href="http://www.marshfarm.co.uk/">Marsh\r\n                                Farm</a><br><br> There are many others we can help with but one we find all the family\r\n                            enjoy, including older children, is<a target="_blank"\r\n                                                                  href="http://www.tropicalwings.co.uk/">&nbsp;Tropical\r\n                                Wings&nbsp;</a><br><a href="/activities" class="link_normal">Read more</a></li>\r\n                        <li><img src="https://www.downhamhall.com/wp-content/themes/animatedone/img/activities_3_thumb.jpg" alt=""\r\n                                 class="img-circle styled"><h4>Explore\r\n                                beautiful gardens</h4>\r\n                            <p>RHS Hyde Hall is in striking distance of Downham Hall. It is a large estate with well\r\n                                manicured gardens and a multitude of events.&nbsp;<a target="_blank"\r\n                                                                                     href="https://www.rhs.org.uk/gardens/hyde-hall">See\r\n                                    more here</a><br><br>There are plenty of other options including Beth Chatto, Audley\r\n                                End House,&nbsp;<a href="/activities" class="link_normal">Read more</a></p></li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="col-md-4">\r\n                    <div class="box_style_1 text-center"><p><img\r\n                                    src="https://www.downhamhall.com/wp-content/themes/animatedone/img/best_price.png" alt=""></p>\r\n                        <p>We plan to run a high quality but affordable property that is attractive for individuals on\r\n                            business, couples enjoying a break and also families with children of all ages.</p>\r\n                        <p>As owners, we have been all of the above and know what each is looking for and will be on\r\n                            hand to help with everything you need.</p></div><!-- End box_style_1--><a href="about"\r\n                                                                                                      class="box_style_1 weahter"><i\r\n                                class="icon-light-up"></i> View Weather forecast</a><!-- End  weather-->\r\n                    <div id="banner"><h3><span>Free wine</span>Free bottle of wine for our<br>first 10 bookings</h3>\r\n                    </div><!-- End banner--></div>\r\n            </div><!-- End row--></div><!-- End container-->\r\n        <div class="container-fluid">\r\n            <div class="row">\r\n                <div class="col-md-6 nopadding">\r\n                    <div class="features-bg">\r\n                        <div class="features-img"></div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class="col-md-6 nopadding">\r\n                    <div class="features-content"><h3>"Enjoy spectacular countryside"</h3>\r\n                        <p>We are so lucky to be surrounded in all directions by rolling farmland and part of a natural\r\n                            bowl one side and overlooking miles of views the other side. Stunning location that you\r\n                            would feel like we are miles from the nearest town but truly only 5 minutes away.</p>\r\n                        <p><a href="/about" class="btn_1 white">Read more</a></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div><!-- End container-fluid-->', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2018-01-05 15:57:14', '2018-01-05 15:57:14', '', 0, 'https://www.downhamhall.com/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
