(35, 1, '2018-01-05 15:35:43', '2018-01-05 15:35:43', '<section id="bg_weddings" class="sub_header"><div class="sub_header_content"><div class="animated fadeInDown"><h1>Wedding Fair - September 10th 2017</h1><p>Downham Hall Wedding Fair Essex</p></div></div></section>\r\n<div id="position"><div class="container"><ul><li><a href="/">Home</a></li><li><a href="undefined">Weddings</a></li><li>Wedding Fair</li></ul></div></div>\r\n<div class="container margin_60">\r\n<div class="main_title">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Wedding Fair Sunday 10th September 2017</h2>\r\n<p class="lead">We will be open from 11-3 and have a range of suppliers in attendance</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-9"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-8">\r\n\r\nWe are delighted to be holding our first Wedding Fair at Downham Hall on Sunday 10th\r\nSeptember between 11 and 3pm.\r\n\r\nOffering a very bespoke wedding for your special day, Downham Hall will give you that little something which will make your wedding day unique and set apart from the rest.\r\n\r\nComplimentary drinks will be provided as well as our top suppliers to chat with about your big day. Come and have a look around this stunning venue and join us for an informal chat and get a feel for this\r\nmagical venue.The marquee will be set up as it would be for your big day and a range of different tables and set ups will give you some great ideas to take away.\r\n\r\nThe owners and all the team will be on hand to answer any questions you may have and will create the perfect package to suit your needs on your special day.\r\n\r\nAll suppliers included are listed below:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Michael Frank jewellers</li>\r\n 	<li>Pinkface cakes</li>\r\n 	<li>TJ designer weddings</li>\r\n 	<li>Marquee overlooking the moat and countryside below</li>\r\n 	<li>Images beautique</li>\r\n 	<li>PureImage Photography</li>\r\n 	<li>Executive cars</li>\r\n 	<li>Roll out the bunting</li>\r\n 	<li>Keekies carts</li