(52, 1, '2018-01-05 15:48:20', '2018-01-05 15:48:20', '<div class="container margin_60 padd_bottom_20">\r\n<div class="main_title">\r\n\r\n<!--span-->\r\n<h2>Downham Hall is a new Wedding Venue in Essex</h2>\r\nCurrently preparing to open for weddings with our introductory Wedding Fair on 10th September 2017. We\r\nare very excited to make our first presentation, nervous too with all the hard work but people who have seen it\r\nso far, generally fall in love with the place, just like we have and hope you will too.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="box_home">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Brochure and Pricing</h3>\r\n<strong>We have put together our first brochure and pricing structure and it is available to\r\ndownload</strong><a href="/downloads/downham-hall-brochure.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> here </a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="box_home">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Celebrate in style</h3>\r\nWith so many places to enjoy with your guests, share a drink and take photos. You will have a day\r\nto remember.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="box_home">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Accommodation available</h3>\r\nDownham Hall has 5 rooms that will be available for wedding guests including a large Bridal\r\nSuite.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- End row-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- End container-->\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class="container add_bottom_60">\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Your special day</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Located in rural Essex, within easy access of the A12, A127 and just 20 minutes from the M25, family run Downham Hall is a perfect venue to gather friends and loved ones. The stunning and lovingly restored Hall is surrounded by beautiful countryside and situated at the bottom of a hill, providing an all round panoramic view of the surrounding area. The Hall is set apart from civilisation by a charming country lane and all who come to visit are impressed by the beautiful facade and grand entranceway upon arrival.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">This part-moated Hall is a fabulous venue for your wedding day, offering plenty of opportunities for those picture postcard shots of your special day. It is currently being refurbished to a very high standard and every detail is considered in our planning and design to ensure your special day runs smoothly and you have a wonderful stay here at Downham Hall.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">When you choose Downham Hall, you will enjoy exclusive use of the Hall and we will be offering five individually designed luxurious bedrooms all with en suites and breathtaking views, as well as a bridal changing room overlooking the gardens. Breakfast is provided the following morning, allowing you time to\r\nenjoy being with family and friends after your special day.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We have a fabulous entrance hall to welcome guests and in winter time the fireplace is a fantastic backdrop to some great photo opportunities. The function room will hold up to 50 guests seated and the orangery is a great place to take in the views of the garden. There are several seated areas including a patio, raised decking area and further seating provided on the south side of the Hall overlooking the moat. For larger groups we offer a marquee within the grounds on the south side of the Hall.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">The church which overlooks Downham Hall at the top of the hill is a beautiful place to have a wedding ceremony and is within throwing distance of the venue. There are also several other places for ceremonies to take place both inside and outside of the Hall itself within the grounds. We are currently applying for a\r\nwedding licence for various locations within the Hall and grounds.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We pride ourselves in seeking the very best in everything connected to our venue and have sought out the best suppliers, offering excellent service in a relaxed atmosphere.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Our wedding co-ordinators will be available from the very first booking to answer all questions and provide a guiding hand throughout the planning phase through to the special day itself.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">This boutique venue is the perfect place to begin married life together and offers the following:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="list_ok">\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;">Part-moated Hall with exclusive hire of the venue</li>\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;">5 bedrooms all with en suite</li>\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;">Bridal changing room</li>\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;">Marquee overlooking the moat and countryside below</li>\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;">On site parking</li>\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;">Wedding co-ordinator throughout all the preparation phase and help on hand during the day</li>\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;">Excellent suppliers recommended to you by the Downham Hall team</li>\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;">Tailor made packages to suit the individual couple and their requirements</li>\r\n 	<li style="text-align: left;"><a href="/wedding-same-sex">Same sex weddings welcome</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class="container add_bottom_60">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div id="strip_activities" class="col-md-8">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><img class="img-circle styled" src="https://www.downhamhall.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/ourphilosophy.jpg" alt="Our wedding philosophy" />\r\n<h4>Our philosophy</h4>\r\nWe believe that a wedding should be fun on\r\nthe day and that you can look back happily and know that all your guests had a great time. We\r\nappreciate that weddings can be very stressful and encourage you to resist the stress and\r\nheighten the excitement. Good food, good friends around you, great photos, and a relaxed order\r\nto the day with some lovely, incredibly special details will make it your perfect day.\r\nWe are being very selective with suppliers as they are a key factor in the success of any\r\nwedding and have spent a lot of time meeting and gaining feedback on the ones we have chosen to\r\nwork with.\r\nRead more<a href="/wedding-philosophy"> here</a></li>\r\n 	<li><img class="img-circle styled" src="https://www.downhamhall.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/ourgrounds.jpg" alt="Our wedding grounds" />\r\n<h4>Our grounds</h4>\r\nWe have been incredibly proud of the progress already made in the gardens and\r\nsimply cutting down the growth has revealed the intrisic relationship with the beautiful\r\ncountryside all around. The panoramic views range from immediate crop or cow filled fields down\r\nto the Thames Estuary and Kent in the distance beyond.</li>\r\n 	<li><img class="img-circle styled" src="https://www.downhamhall.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/ourfunctionrooms.jpg" alt="Our function rooms" />\r\n<h4>Our Function Rooms</h4>\r\nWe aim to offer three distinct inside spaces, our lobby with historic fireplace, our large\r\nfunction room and stunning Orangery overlooking the gardens and basin like countryside. All\r\nare being renovated right now but we have visual plans and progress every day.<a class="link_normal" href="/wedding-function-rooms">Read more</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4">\r\n<div class="box_style_1 text-center">\r\n<div class="badge">\r\n<div class="badgeInner">\r\n\r\n<a class="company-name" href="https://www.hitched.co.uk/wedding-venues/downham-hall_7603.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Downham Hall</a>\r\n<div class="featuredOn"><a href="https://www.hitched.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">As featured\r\non</a></div>\r\n<a href="https://www.hitched.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img title="hitched.co.uk" src="//images.hitched.co.uk/logos/hitched.png" alt="hitched.co.uk" border="0" /></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- End box_style_1-->\r\n<div id="banner">\r\n<h3>Our brochure <a href="/downloads/downham-hall-brochure.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download</a></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- End banner-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- End row-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- End container-->\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Weddings', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '24-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-05 15:48:20', '2018-01-05 15:48:20', '', 24, 'https://www.downhamhall.com/2018/01/05/24-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(53, 1, '2018-01-05 15:49:41', '2018-01-05 15:49:41', '<section id="bg_weddings" class="sub_header"><div class="sub_header_content"><div class="animated fadeInDown"><h1>Wedding Licenses</h1><p>Downham Hall Wedding Licenses</p></div></div></section>\r\n<div id="position"><div class="container"><ul><li><a href="/">Home</a></li><li><a href="undefined">Weddings</a></li><li>Wedding Licenses</li></ul></div></div>\r\n<div class="container margin_60"><div class="main_title"><span></span><h2>Wedding Licenses</h2><p class="lead">As a new venue we want to give some information about our licenses</p></div><div class="row"><div class="col-md-9"></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-md-12"><p>We are still in a development phase and as a result are not currently in a position to secure our wedding licence. We will be applying to be able to marry people on site as soon as we can but that will take a short period of time.</p>\r\n<p> A licence requires finished fire regulations and parking places among more obvious things around 3 sided structures for people to marry in. This is all underway in readiness for our application.</p></div></div></div>\r\n', 'Licenses', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'wedding-licenses', '', '', '2018-01-05 15:50:52', '2018-01-05 15:50:52', '', 0, 'https://www.downhamhall.com/?page_id=53', 0, 'page', '', 0),
